@tcmxx I finally got back from vacation and tried out your file! It actually worked! Nice. Thank you. Although I got the following message in the output. Seems that my Cuda capability is 3.5. Time for a new graphics card upgrade??

**OUTPUT:**
```
Hello from 1.3.0-rc2

name: Quadro K5200 major: 3 minor: 5 memoryClockRate(GHz): 0.771

The minimum required Cuda capability is 3.7.**
